It works just perfect but i don't see improvements over the free google earth. 
I should say that i only looked at the images of my city (unfocusable) and an other one that is focusable.

The reason why some cities are not focusable is to protect privacy and it was done that way at the request of the city authorities.

So, the software is not at fault.
